74
00:09:25.800 --> 00:09:26.835
Ah. good times. huh?

75
00:09:26.960 --> 00:09:28.997
Tell you what.
we'll do this again. huh.

76
00:09:29.920 --> 00:09:30.910
Yeah!

77
