86
00:12:39.520 --> 00:12:41.989
I'll be turning it
over to Vice and Narcotics.

87
00:12:44.680 --> 00:12:46.432
We didn't know our own son.

88
00:12:52.800 --> 00:12:54.279
Kyle wasn't a druggie.

89
00:12:54.360 --> 00:12:57.034
