127
00:18:32.200 --> 00:18:36.353
He worked at the Kehoe airport
with my son... Kyle.

128
00:18:37.800 --> 00:18:38.790
You know him too.

129
00:18:43.640 --> 00:18:44.630
Kyle?

130
00:18:46.560 --> 00:18:49.029
Oh. yeah. Kyle. that's your kid?

131
00:18:50.040 --> 00:18:52.998
Yeah. yeah. I. uh...
No. I don't know him. Sorry.

132
00:18:54.080 --> 00:18:57.277
