161
00:23:21.920 --> 00:23:24.639
One of my employees.
But you wouldn't know about him.

162
00:23:24.720 --> 00:23:28.350
because we don't talk about business
on the way to school. do we?

163
00:23:39.080 --> 00:23:40.275
Who packed these?

164
00:23:43.440 --> 00:23:46.159
- Didn't think a treat would kill him.
- High fructose corn syrup.

165
00:23:46.560 --> 00:23:47.550
Lecithin.

166
00:23:48.520 --> 00:23:49.510
Baking soda?

167
00:23:51.800 --> 00:23:53.950
The only thing not in those is rat poison.

168
00:23:57.600 --> 00:23:58.590
I want you to know...

169
00:24:00.120 --> 00:24:01.599
