187
00:25:13.640 --> 00:25:15.995
Yeah. it's legal to purchase.
legal to smoke at home.

188
00:25:16.080 --> 00:25:17.593
Take a breath. Come on. breathe.

189
00:25:18.360 --> 00:25:20.476
There's a principle
you need to get on board with

190
00:25:20.560 --> 00:25:24.633
