Guess it's just every man
for himself in there.

592
01:00:45.200 --> 01:00:47.840
You see. out here. character counts.

593
01:00:48.200 --> 01:00:51.113
Without character there can be
no business and...

594
01:00:51.600 --> 01:00:52.954
without business...

595
01:00:54.400 --> 01:00:55.390
well...

596
01:00:57.360 --> 01:00:59.033
what the hell would we do all day?

597
01:01:16.840 --> 01:01:18.513
Would you mind stepping off the rug?

598
