You're gonna take me to Dublin?

606
01:02:13.600 --> 01:02:14.590
Yeah.

607
01:02:17.640 --> 01:02:18.630
Hey.

608
01:02:24.560 --> 01:02:26.153
Mustang. if we get caught out.

609
