618
01:04:21.480 --> 01:04:24.632
The only question is.
how much pain do you wanna endure?

619
01:04:24.720 --> 01:04:29.476
I got cancer of the ass. dickweed.
So screw you. and screw your pain.

620
01:04:30.320 --> 01:04:32.038
You wanna know what this is all about?

621
