658
01:07:05.120 --> 01:07:07.077
I could probably be done
with them by tonight.

659
01:07:07.800 --> 01:07:12.078
And then I could put
all my pent up energy into something else.

660
01:07:12.600 --> 01:07:13.590
<i>Hmm.</i>

661
01:07:14.480 --> 01:07:17.598
<i>Okay. well. you got them. baby. Bang.</i>

662
01:07:17.720 --> 01:07:18.994
<i>Right in your inbox.</i>

663
01:07:19.600 --> 01:07:20.829
Oh. they're right in there.

664
01:07:20.920 --> 01:07:23.230
<i>So. how do we wanna do this?</i>

665
01:07:23.640 --> 01:07:26.234
<i>I'm thinking you leave the door open
