666
01:07:26.760 --> 01:07:28.034
<i>Trust me to find...</i>

667
01:07:29.840 --> 01:07:31.672
Hold on a second. What was that?

668
01:07:31.960 --> 01:07:34.110
- I said...
- Oh God. we got an avalanche.

669
