See if it all comes back to you.

714
01:11:15.600 --> 01:11:17.637
They needed a host
for next week's fundraiser.

715
01:11:18.160 --> 01:11:19.195
I signed you UP-

716
01:12:33.840 --> 01:12:35.877
- Here.
- Three of Viking's drug dealers

717
