And my guess is White Bull's
not gonna like that.

727
01:13:07.560 --> 01:13:11.713
So. has anyone got any ideas on
how we might set things right?

728
01:13:11.800 --> 01:13:13.871
Yeah. maybe we should apologize.

729
01:13:14.800 --> 01:13:15.790
Yeah?

730
