One little screw up
shouldn't make us their bitches.

731
01:13:18.840 --> 01:13:20.558
So we send them a short note.

732
01:13:20.640 --> 01:13:23.792
Hey. and what does
this. uh. short note say?

733
01:13:23.920 --> 01:13:25.240
I don't know. How about.

734
