with a bit more oomph.

737
01:13:35.880 --> 01:13:36.995
Something from our heart.

738
01:13:55.040 --> 01:13:57.839
Yeah. cut off his head.
Stick it in a box and send it to them.

739
01:13:57.920 --> 01:13:59.274
Tell them he's the culprit.

740
01:13:59.360 --> 01:14:03.593
Tell them our old arrangement's
back in effect and good to go.

741
01:14:16.720 --> 01:14:18.518
Get that shit away from me. man.

742
01:14:19.200 --> 01:14:20.599
What the hell's wrong with you?

743
01:14:22.400 --> 01:14:26.314
We've got some of the best pot stores
in the world. man. All legal.

744
01:14:26.640 --> 01:14:29.917
But no. instead you choose to smoke
that dang reservation weed.

745
01:14:31.320 --> 01:14:32.594
Maybe I like it better.

746
01:14:36.880 --> 01:14:39.156
- White people. man.
- Yeah.

747
01:14:41.720 --> 01:14:44.234
You know I had a rat
that was bigger than that thing.

748
01:14:49.280 --> 01:14:51.590
You should try smoking that shit instead.

749
01:14:52.640 --> 01:14:53.710
That's gross.

750
01:14:57.800 --> 01:14:58.790
Mom!

751
