753
01:15:11.880 --> 01:15:12.870
Damn.

754
01:15:15.800 --> 01:15:17.757
- Kehoe.
- Hey. <i>it's Kurt.</i>

755
01:15:19.400 --> 01:15:21.311
Hi. Kurt.

756
01:15:21.400 --> 01:15:22.993
<i>You don't deserve this intel.</i>

757
01:15:25.360 --> 01:15:27.874
<i>- Intel?
