759
01:15:31.600 --> 01:15:35.912
<i>A body. Dante Ferstel. Kehoe kid.
Found dead in a Denver alley.</i>

760
01:15:36.000 --> 01:15:38.150
<i>Smack overdose. So. what's new. right?</i>

761
01:15:38.240 --> 01:15:39.833
<i>Just another Saturday night sleeper.</i>

762
01:15:40.280 --> 01:15:41.270
<i>And here's the kicker.</i>

763
01:15:41.680 --> 01:15:43.990
<i>Dante was a baggage monkey at the airport.</i>

